History
-------

git-bzr was originally implementedin Ruby by frimmirf@gmail.com, and
improvements were added by Pieter de Bie <pdebie@ai.rug.nl>.

Bash version
------------

git-bzr was converted to bash by Matej Cepl <mcepl@redhat.com>

Further improvements have been made by:

